@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultTextAlignment left
skinparam ArrowColor #1F2937
skinparam rectangle {
  FontColor #111827
  BorderColor #1F2937
}
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEE2E2
skinparam NoteBorderColor #B91C1C

title React Tests Before: Duplicate React Singleton

rectangle "node --import tsx --test" as Runner #DBEAFE
rectangle "react-test-renderer\n(require('react'))" as RTR #FECACA
rectangle "SDK/Test imports\n(import 'react')" as SDK #FECACA
rectangle "Hooks Runtime" as Runtime #E5E7EB

Runner --> RTR
Runner --> SDK
RTR --> Runtime : React instance A
SDK --> Runtime : React instance B

note right of Runtime
On Windows + pnpm symlink casing,
two module cache keys are created for React.
Hooks dispatcher mismatch triggers:
"Invalid hook call"
end note
@enduml
